lines.text: Exalt  the Lord our God (Exalt  the Lord our God)
And worship at His feet (And worship at His feet)
For the Lord our God, He is* holy
For the Lord our God, He is holy
For the Lord our God, He is holy
Yes the Lord our God, He is holy
